00:48:49,540 --> 00:48:53,380
高斯丁是我一年紀的指導教授
Noah Goldstein was my counselor my freshman year.

499
00:48:53,450 --> 00:48:56,680
我的冰錐靈感大概就由此而來 在我書中
That's probably where I got the idea for the ice pick for my book.

500
00:48:58,750 --> 00:49:01,220
潛意識的力量真是驚人
Funny how the subconscious works.

501
00:49:01,320 --> 00:49:02,580
的確
Hilarious.

502
00:49:04,790 --> 00:49:08,730
-艾索是我的朋友. -你的朋友把一家人全宰了
- Hazel's my friend. - Your friend took out her whole family.

503
00:49:08,800 --> 00:49:11,890
她使我了解殺人的沖動
Yes,she helped me understand homicidal impulse.

504
00:49:12,300 --> 00:49:14,100
你在學校就學到了
I thought you would have learned that at school.

505
00:49:15,670 --> 00:49:17,640
只是理論上的
Only in theory.

506
00:49:17,670 --> 00:49:22,910
你對殺人沖動了解十分透徹. 不是嗎，槍手？
But you know all about homicidal impulse,don't you,shooter?

507
00:49:25,480 --> 00:49:27,910
不是理論，是實務的
Not in theory,in practice.

508
00:49:28,250 --> 00:49:31,690
卷入其中的滋味如何？
What happened? Did you get sucked into it?

509
00:49:31,750 --> 00:49:34,550
你無法自拔嗎？
Did you like it too much?

510
00:49:36,520 --> 00:49:39,360
我不知道你在說什麼
I don't know what you're talking about.

511
00:49:41,300 --> 00:49:43,700
談談可卡因吧，尼克
Tell me about the coke,Nick.

512
00:49:45,800 --> 00:49:48,770
你殺了觀光客的那天…
The day you shot those two tourists...

513
00:49:48,840 --> 00:49:50,810
你吸了多少可卡因？
how much coke did you do?

514
00:49:54,580 --> 00:49:57,810
你可以告訴我
Come on,you can tell me.

515
00:50:03,750 --> 00:50:07,550
-我吸了. -你吸了…
- I didn't. - Yes,you did.

516
00:50:07,660 --> 00:50:10,890
他們沒替你檢驗
They never tested you,did they?

517
00:50:11,130 --> 00:50:13,890
風紀組的人知道
Internal Affairs knew.

518
00:50:16,130 --> 00:50:19,290
你老婆也知道，對不對？
Your wife knew too,didn't she?

519
00:50:24,510 --> 00:50:26,800
她知道怎麼回事
She knew what was going on.

520
00:50:29,640 --> 00:50:31,670
你離火焰太近了
I think you got too close to the flame.

521
00:50:39,620 --> 00:50:41,650
我想你很喜歡
I think you liked it.

522
00:50:46,330 --> 00:50:48,800
所以她才自殺
That's why she killed herself.

523
00:51:04,380 --> 00:51:06,180
嗨，海倫
Hi,hon.

524
00:51:10,420 --> 00:51:13,650
你們兩位見過面
You two have met,haven't you?

525
00:51:22,460 --> 00:51:25,800
你會是位了不起的角色
You're gonna make a terrific character,Nick.

526
00:51:34,710 --> 00:51:38,580
她正在打電話，馬上會叫你
She's on the phone. She'll be right with you.

527
00:51:38,680 --> 00:51:43,140
-我馬上會打回去給你. -探長，你不能進去--
- I'm gonna have to call you back. - Detective,you can't go in...

528
00:51:43,380 --> 00:51:45,720
-誰動過我的檔案？ -你在說什麼？
- Who's got access to my file? - What are you talking about?

529
00:51:45,790 --> 00:51:47,880
誰動過我那些檔案？
Who has access to my goddamn file?

530
00:51:48,160 --> 00:51:51,750
沒人動過. 那些是機密的個人心理資料
Nobody. It's a confidential psychiatric record. It would be illegal.

531
00:51:51,860 --> 00:51:54,560
你干的，少對我扯謊言
Don't you fucking lie to me!

532
00:51:54,630 --> 00:51:56,620
是風紀組動的
It was Internal Affairs,wasn't it?

533
00:51:56,700 --> 00:51:57,720
不是的
No,please.

534
00:51:57,800 --> 00:52:00,790
-是誰？ -是尼爾森
- Who? - It's Nilson.

535
00:52:12,610 --> 00:52:14,380
有何貴干，柯倫？
What do you want,Curran?

536
00:52:14,450 --> 00:52:15,680
你把我的檔案賣了
You sold her my file,didn't you?

537
00:52:15,780 --> 00:52:17,840
你在說誰？
Who are you talking about?

538
00:52:18,090 --> 00:52:21,520
凱瑟琳楚梅. 她付你多少？
Catherine Tramell. How much did she pay you?

539
00:52:21,590 --> 00:52:25,120
快點住手
Hey,Curran,come on! Damn it,stop it!

540
00:52:25,190 --> 00:52:26,520
多少錢？
How much?

541
00:52:28,630 --> 00:52:32,460
快住手，柯倫！
Hey,back off! Back off,Curran!

542
00:52:32,530 --> 00:52:35,590
輕松一點
Nice and easy now. Nice and easy.

543
00:52:35,670 --> 00:52:38,610
去你媽的頭，你完蛋了
You fucked yourself,shooter. You hear me? You are out!

544
00:52:38,670 --> 00:52:41,440
-柯倫，輕松點. -你死定了！
- Curran,take it easy. - You are out!

545
00:52:42,840 --> 00:52:44,470
省省吧
Save it,save it.

546
00:52:47,820 --> 00:52:50,180
-尼克，你沒事吧？ -我沒事
- What's going down,Hoss? - Nothing. I'll be okay.

547
00:52:50,420 --> 00:52:53,510
-他們不會放過你的. -我痛恨被人耍著玩
- They're gonna want your badge. - I'm tired of being played with.

548
00:52:53,590 --> 00:52:56,110
你表現的方式真是與眾不同
You got a real conclusive way of demonstrating that.

549
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:05,600
她把我摸的一清二楚
She knows where I live and breathe.

550
00:53:07,500 --> 00:53:09,270
我被她盯上了，加斯
She's coming after me,Gus.

551
00:53:10,270 --> 00:53:12,170
她和你有什麼瓜葛？
What is it you got between you?

552
00:53:15,610 --> 00:53:19,640
-我不知道. -是有點不對
- I don't know. - Something,though.

553
00:53:19,710 --> 00:53:22,770
是的，沒錯
Something.

554
00:53:32,460 --> 00:53:36,520
TV:GeorgeJefferson is unfair. He's short with no hair.

555
00:53:41,900 --> 00:53:43,840
尼克，你在裡面嗎？
Nick,are you there?

556
00:53:43,910 --> 00:53:46,810
走開.貝絲，我不想見你
Go away,Beth. I don't want to see you.

557
00:53:53,210 --> 00:53:55,840
我還有鑰匙
I still have my key.

558
00:53:57,650 --> 00:53:59,590
放在桌上然後離開
Put them on the table and leave.

559
00:54:02,490 --> 00:54:05,080
放在他媽的桌上快離開！
Put them on the goddamn table and leave!

560
00:54:05,190 --> 00:54:08,160
媽的！別轟我出去. 你欠我的不只是這些
Damn it! Don't shove me out! You owe me more than that!

561
00:54:10,630 --> 00:54:13,260
我什麼也不欠你！
I don't owe you anything!

562
00:54:13,330 --> 00:54:16,130
你也不欠我什麼
And you don't owe me anything.

563
00:54:16,200 --> 00:54:19,300
我們是有上床，大概十到十五次
We went to bed,what,10,15 times?

564
00:54:19,510 --> 00:54:23,140
那可不是我的責任
It wasn't memorable enough to carry an obligation.

565
00:54:24,880 --> 00:54:27,540
有時候我真的很恨你
Sometimes I really hate you.

566
00:54:27,650 --> 00:54:30,550
你為何不替自己開些藥方…
Why don't you get yourself some friendly little therapist...

567
00:54:30,620 --> 00:54:32,880
讓自己溫柔一點？
to work out some of that hostility?

568
00:54:33,090 --> 00:54:36,180
或許能有些用處
And maybe you can get off once in a while.

569
00:54:39,160 --> 00:54:41,750
你這神經病
Are you nuts?

570
00:54:50,910 --> 00:54:52,340
對不起
I'm sorry.

571
00:54:54,680 --> 00:54:57,200
我很少這個樣子
I don't usually act like that.

572
00:54:57,310 --> 00:54:59,910
你怎麼把我的檔案流出去？
How could you give him my file?

573
00:55:00,150 --> 00:55:01,620
我是被迫的！
I had to!

574
00:55:01,720 --> 00:55:05,580
他打算將你從局裡除名
He was going to recommend your discharge from the force.

575
00:55:05,650 --> 00:55:08,880
他也不接受我的評估 認為不夠客觀
He didn't buy my evaluation. He said I wasn't objective.

576
00:55:09,120 --> 00:55:12,750
所以我拿那個和他作交換條件
So I made a deal with him to review the session notes himself.

577
00:55:12,860 --> 00:55:15,260
我沒想到他會給別人看
I didn't think he'd show them to anybody.

578
00:55:15,330 --> 00:55:18,160
-你是為了我？ -是的
- You did it for me? - Yes.

579
00:55:18,270 --> 00:55:20,730
因為我關心你. 才為你這樣做
I care about you. I did it for you.

580
00:55:26,210 --> 00:55:29,640
你走吧，拜托你快走
Go away. Please,just go away.

581
00:55:58,440 --> 00:56:00,370
喂。
Yo.

582
00:56:04,310 --> 00:56:07,210
我馬上趕去
I'm on my way.

583
00:56:57,430 --> 00:57:01,800
一槍斃命，近距離射擊. 大概是點三八左輪
One shot. Close range. Probably a.38 caliber revolver.

584
00:57:03,300 --> 00:57:05,700
你的槍給我，尼克
Give me your gun,Nick.

585
00:57:14,780 --> 00:57:17,380
你以為--
You think that...

586
00:57:21,290 --> 00:57:25,120
我不認為是你. 但我的意見是少數
I don't,Hoss. But I got the minority opinion.

587
00:57:29,830 --> 00:57:34,130
是的，我討厭他！ 我一時失去控制
Okay,I went after him! I lost my temper.

588
00:57:34,240 --> 00:57:37,230
你有證據他把你的心理檔案 給別人看嗎？
Do you have any evidence that he showed your psychiatric file to anyone?

589
00:57:44,210 --> 00:57:46,150
等一下會找你談，嘉納大夫
We'll speak with you afterwards,Dr. Garner.

590
00:57:46,210 --> 00:57:48,200
-我想參加，不介意吧. -我想你還是--
- I'd like to sit in. - I'd really rather wait...

591
00:57:48,280 --> 00:57:52,180
我想有她在座應該無所謂， 柯倫探長不反對的話
It's all right if Dr. Garner sits in, if Detective Curran doesn't object.

592
00:57:58,090 --> 00:58:01,080
-你昨晚人在何處？ -在家看電視
- Where were you last night? - Home,watching TV.

593
00:58:01,160 --> 00:58:02,750
整晚都在？
All night?

594
00:58:03,530 --> 00:58:05,160
是的，一整晚
Yes,all night.

595
00:58:05,230 --> 00:58:07,430
在喝酒嗎？
Were you drinking?

596
00:58:11,170 --> 00:58:12,760
是的，喝了一點
Yeah,I was drinking.

597
00:58:12,840 --> 00:58:15,740
-你何時有開始喝的？ -幾天前
- When did you start drinking again? - A couple of days ago.

598
00:58:15,840 --> 00:58:19,280
大約昨晚十點左右 我看見他在家裡
I saw Detective Curran at his apartment about 10:00 last night.

599
00:58:19,350 --> 00:58:21,250
他當時神智清醒
He was sober and lucid.

600
00:58:21,320 --> 00:58:23,840
我問他對尼爾森警官的感受
I asked him,in my capacity as his departmental therapist...

601
00:58:24,090 --> 00:58:26,180
我問他對尼爾森警官的感受
about his altercation with Lieutenant Nilsen.

602
00:58:26,290 --> 00:58:29,420
他深表悔意
He expressed regret and displayed no hostility.

603
00:58:29,520 --> 00:58:33,430
-你在他公寓待了多久？ -大約十五分鍾
- How long were you at his apartment? - About 15 minutes.

604
00:58:33,460 --> 00:58:36,830
直到我放心了才離去
I saw there was no reason for my concern and left.

605
00:58:36,900 --> 00:58:39,560
這裡不能吸煙的
There's no smoking in this building,Detective.

606
00:58:41,770 --> 00:58:43,570
你想告我吸煙嗎？
What are you gonna do? Charge me with smoking?

607
00:58:45,510 --> 00:58:49,170
天哪--尼克，我再問你一次就夠了
Oh,for Christ's... All right,Nick, I'm gonna ask you this just once.

608
00:58:49,280 --> 00:58:52,470
為了記錄，你是否殺了尼爾森？
For the record, did you kill Marty Nilsen?

609
00:58:54,350 --> 00:58:56,410
沒有
No.

610
00:58:56,480 --> 00:58:59,180
我不會當著大家的面先詛咒他…
I'm gonna storm into his office in front of everybody...

611
00:58:59,290 --> 00:59:01,220
然後當晚把他宰了
in the middle of the day and kill him that night?

612
00:59:01,290 --> 00:59:03,280
我沒那麼笨
I'm not that dumb.

613
00:59:03,360 --> 00:59:07,260
你先離去 再回頭殺他正好可脫罪. 那是你的不在場證明
Going after him before gets you off the hook for killing him. That's your alibi.

614
00:59:07,330 --> 00:59:10,790
你也是看書學來的這一套
Like writing a book about killing a guy gets you off the hook for killing him.

615
00:59:10,900 --> 00:59:11,870
說的好
Good point.

616
00:59:12,100 --> 00:59:13,830
我不懂你在說什麼書
What are you talking about?

617
00:59:13,900 --> 00:59:17,430
-這是我們自己的笑話，混賬. -我不覺得好笑
- A private joke,asshole. - I don't think it's funny.

618
00:59:17,510 --> 00:59:18,840
你的職務暫時被吊銷…
You're going on leave...

619
00:59:19,910 --> 00:59:23,340
繼續進行心理狀態評估
pending the outcome of a psychiatric evaluation.

620
00:59:35,390 --> 00:59:37,860
貝絲，我馬上回來拿行李
I'll get my stuff in a minute.

621
00:59:42,460 --> 00:59:43,560
謝謝你
Thank you.

622
00:59:48,240 --> 00:59:50,290
我至少能幫上這個忙
It's the least I could do.

623
00:59:50,400 --> 00:59:53,200
是我害你來問話的
Considering I got you into this mess with those reports.

624
00:59:53,270 --> 00:59:55,830
我是說真的，謝謝
No,I mean it. Thank you.

625
00:59:57,810 --> 01:00:00,580
你怎知道凱瑟琳看過你的檔案？
How do you know Catherine Tramell saw your file?

626
01:00:00,820 --> 01:00:04,440
她知道一些事， 我只告訴過你
She knows things about me that I only told you.

627
01:00:04,520 --> 01:00:07,110
一定有什麼不對
She must really be something.

628
01:00:07,220 --> 01:00:09,450
從治療的觀點來看
From a clinical point of view.

629
01:00:09,520 --> 01:00:12,390
-她在學校表現如何？ -我跟她不熟
- What was she like in school? - I hardly knew her.

630
01:00:12,460 --> 01:00:14,160
她讓我有些毛骨悚然
She gave me the creeps.

631
01:00:14,230 --> 01:00:16,160
不知道為什麼
I don't know why.

632
01:00:20,330 --> 01:00:23,330
休息一下.答應我
Get some rest. Promise?

633
01:00:29,210 --> 01:00:32,340
-我昨天說的那些話不是認真的-- -你是的
- I didn't mean what I said about... - Yes,you did.

634
01:00:32,410 --> 01:00:35,380
我不是小孩子，我會處理的
I'm a big girl. I can handle it.

635
01:00:59,170 --> 01:01:02,370
-你自己多保重. -你對她父母的調查怎樣？
- You take care of yourself. - What'd you find out about the parents?

636
01:01:02,440 --> 01:01:05,340
別提了
No lead,man.

637
01:01:05,380 --> 01:01:08,510
你簡直是神經病
You're on psycho leave. I'm talking to a possible wacko!

638
01:01:08,580 --> 01:01:11,520
你知道我神經病，到底怎樣？
You know I'm wacko. What'd you find out?

639
01:01:15,260 --> 01:01:18,660
游艇爆炸. 燃料箱漏洞
The boat blew. There was a leak in the fuel line.

640
01:01:18,890 --> 01:01:22,660
曾經修理過兩次 兩人投了高額的保險
There were two previous repairs and a five mil policy on both of them.

641
01:01:22,900 --> 01:01:25,260
曾經積極的調查都沒結果
A real heavy investigation but they got zilch.

642
01:01:25,300 --> 01:01:28,100
賠了一大筆錢，說是意外
Big goose egg. It was an "accident."

643
01:01:28,170 --> 01:01:31,500
風紀組還要找你問話. 由他們調查，我們不插手
I.A.'s gonna talk to you about Nilsen. They're handling the investigation.

644
01:01:31,570 --> 01:01:34,340
你和嘉納大夫保持聯絡. 對你的評估有幫助
Stay in touch with Dr. Garner. It'll help on the evaluation.

645
01:01:34,410 --> 01:01:37,710
是她干的
She killed him.

646
01:01:38,110 --> 01:01:39,410
你說貝絲殺人？
Beth? Now you've got Beth killing people?

647
01:01:39,510 --> 01:01:41,480
是凱瑟琳殺的
Catherine Tramell. It's part of her game.

648
01:01:41,550 --> 01:01:45,580
你先說她偷了你的檔案， 現在又說她殺了尼爾森？
First you got her stealing your file, now she's killing Nilsen?

649
01:01:45,690 --> 01:01:48,550
少來這一套，看在老天的份上. 找個地方曬曬太陽
Forget about her! Go somewhere,sit in the sun.

650
01:01:48,620 --> 01:01:52,250
-讓你神智清醒一下！ -你不相信嗎？
- Get her the hell out of your system! - You don't buy it,do you?

651
01:01:52,360 --> 01:01:54,450
她知道沒人會相信
She knew nobody'd buy it.

652
01:01:54,560 --> 01:01:58,090
她知道沒人相信我說的話
She knew I'd say she did it and nobody'd buy it!

653
01:01:58,130 --> 01:02:01,400
她把你搞得神經錯亂！ 離她遠一點！
She is screwing with your head! Stay away from her!

654
01:02:28,760 --> 01:02:30,390
那件事我聽說了
I heard what happened.

655
01:02:39,140 --> 01:02:42,130
你沒帶槍看來更帥
What good's a shooter without his gun?

656
01:02:42,240 --> 01:02:45,210
-你到底發現了什麼？ -我有律師
- How exactly did you find out? - I have attorneys.

657
01:02:45,310 --> 01:02:48,280
一些好朋友
They have friends. I have friends.

658
01:02:48,380 --> 01:02:50,710
我請了一大堆律師當朋友
Money buys a lot of attorneys and friends.

659
01:02:51,090 --> 01:02:53,250
我沒辦法，我一文不名…
I wouldn't know about that. I don't have any money...

660
01:02:53,320 --> 01:02:56,760
沒錢請律師朋友， 加斯是唯一的朋友
I don't have any attorneys, and Gus is my only real friend.

661
01:02:57,160 --> 01:02:59,250
我們說的是真正的朋友
I wasn't talking about real friends.

662
01:03:03,630 --> 01:03:06,120
加斯干嘛不喜歡我？
Why doesn't Gus like me?

