01:40:51,270 --> 01:40:53,260
她不經意間說出來的？
She tell you casually?

997
01:40:53,300 --> 01:40:55,570
看來似乎不是安排的？
Make it seem irrelevant?

998
01:40:57,140 --> 01:40:59,130
她在床上告訴你的？
Did she tell you in bed?

999
01:41:01,890 --> 01:41:04,870
我也會這樣做
That's what I'd do.

1000
01:41:07,350 --> 01:41:09,210
你干嘛改名？
Why'd you change your name?

1001
01:41:09,280 --> 01:41:12,280
我結婚了，他叫我貝絲
I got married. He called me "Beth."

1002
01:41:12,350 --> 01:41:14,820
他在沙林納診所執業
He was on staff at the clinic in Salinas.

1003
01:41:14,860 --> 01:41:17,120
沒待了多久
Didn't last long.

1004
01:41:20,300 --> 01:41:23,130
尼克 你以為我會殺人嗎？
Do you really think that I could kill someone?

1005
01:41:23,200 --> 01:41:25,060
我根本沒碰過強尼巴茲！
I never even met Johnny Boz!

1006
01:41:25,170 --> 01:41:28,630
我又有什麼動機殺尼爾森？
And what about Nilsen? What motive would I have to kill him?

1007
01:41:28,870 --> 01:41:31,600
把鎖修好
- You should get that lock fixed. - God...

1008
01:41:31,640 --> 01:41:35,100
她是個魔鬼！ 她聰明絕頂！
She's evil! She's brilliant!

1009
01:42:00,140 --> 01:42:02,600
嚇到你了？
Did I scare you?

1010
01:42:02,700 --> 01:42:05,000
本想給你一個驚喜
I wanted to surprise you.

1011
01:42:05,110 --> 01:42:08,040
-有什麼不對？ -我找到麗莎何伯曼了
- What's wrong? - I found Lisa Hoberman.

1012
01:42:08,110 --> 01:42:10,080
是嗎？她現在怎樣
Oh,you did? What's she doing?

1013
01:42:13,580 --> 01:42:16,180
你不打算告訴我
You're not going to tell me what she's doing.

1014
01:42:16,290 --> 01:42:19,650
-我們到底在玩什麼游戲. -我也是在玩
- I thought we were done playing games. - I did too.

1015
01:42:19,860 --> 01:42:21,580
她說你纏著她不放
She said you got it backwards.

1016
01:42:21,690 --> 01:42:24,280
把頭發染的和她一樣
She said you styled your hair like she did.

1017
01:42:24,560 --> 01:42:26,550
你相信她
And you believed her.

1018
01:42:27,660 --> 01:42:33,230
我曾去校園警局檢舉她
I had to go to the campus police and file a report about her.

1019
01:42:33,300 --> 01:42:36,360
-你八成認為人是我殺的？
I suppose you still think I kill people too?

1020
01:42:38,060 --> 01:42:40,060
不！
No！

1021
01:42:41,080 --> 01:42:42,980
說謊
Liar.

1022
01:42:46,620 --> 01:42:50,210
-你說是哪裡？ -舊金山凶殺組
- Who'd you say you're with? - Homicide,San Francisco.

1023
01:42:52,960 --> 01:42:56,600
在這裡
Here we go.Kind of.

1024
01:42:57,190 --> 01:42:59,680
的確有人報案檢舉麗莎何伯曼， 是在八零年一月
There was a report about Lisa Hoberman, January,1980.

1025
01:42:59,900 --> 01:43:02,360
-但不在這裡. -誰拿去了？
- But it's out of here. - Who's got it?

1026
01:43:03,630 --> 01:43:05,620
你們的人…尼爾森
One of your guys. Nilsen.

1027
01:43:05,730 --> 01:43:08,030
-認識他？ -認識
- You know him? - Yeah.

1028
01:43:08,100 --> 01:43:10,260
謝了
Thanks a lot.

1029
01:43:10,340 --> 01:43:13,270
叫他拿回來. 他拿走一年了
Tell him to bring it back. He's had it a whole year.

1030
01:43:13,780 --> 01:43:16,710
尼爾森拿了檔案又怎樣 你也不知道裡面寫什麼
So Nilsen had a report on Beth. You don't know what was in it.

1031
01:43:16,950 --> 01:43:19,350
-凱瑟琳告訴我了. -她說的話能信嗎
- Catherine told me what was in it. - If she's telling you the truth.

1032
01:43:19,580 --> 01:43:21,170
加斯，你還不明白嗎？
Gus,don't you get it?

1033
01:43:21,250 --> 01:43:23,180
貝絲殺了強尼陷害凱瑟琳…
If Beth killed Johnny Boz to frame Catherine...

1034
01:43:23,250 --> 01:43:25,190
她怕別人知道柏克賴的往事！
she wouldn't want anybody to know what happened in Berkeley!

1035
01:43:25,250 --> 01:43:28,310
但被尼爾森發現了，使她有動機殺他
But Nilsen found out about it. That gives her the motive to kill him.

1036
01:43:28,560 --> 01:43:31,360
她怎麼知道尼爾森發現了？
How did she know Nilsen found out, if it happened?

1037
01:43:31,590 --> 01:43:33,750
他是風紀組長，或許他去問她！
He probably asked her!

1038
01:43:33,960 --> 01:43:36,360
她一點也不象是神經病！
She'd have to be nuttier than a 20 pound fruitcake!

1039
01:43:36,630 --> 01:43:39,330
她也不象是連環殺人狂！
She's not the one who hangs out with multiple murderers!

1040
01:43:39,570 --> 01:43:41,970
-是你女朋友干的！ -她是作家，那是她的工作！
- You're girlfriend is! - She's a writer! That's her job!

1041
01:43:42,070 --> 01:43:45,160
我才不信 柏克萊一定有人知道真相
I don't buy it. There must be somebody at Berkeley who knows what happened!

1042
01:43:45,240 --> 01:43:47,170
我知道真相！凱瑟琳說的！
I know what happened! Catherine told me!

1043
01:43:47,240 --> 01:43:50,300
- 我都去查過了！    - 你真的是...
- Everything she says has checked out! - You got tweety birds...

1044
01:43:50,580 --> 01:43:52,600
 操B操昏頭了！
fluttering around in your head!

1045
01:43:52,680 --> 01:43:54,740
你認為你可以隨便亂搞
You think you can fuck like minks, raise rug rats...

1046
01:43:54,950 --> 01:43:56,780
然後永遠逍遙自在嗎？
and live happily ever after?

1047
01:43:56,990 --> 01:43:58,780
少來了！
Oh,man!

1048
01:44:11,030 --> 01:44:13,630
你怎麼進來的？
How'd you get in here?

1049
01:44:13,700 --> 01:44:15,360
這是什麼？
What's this?

1050
01:44:15,600 --> 01:44:18,660
我決定再給你一次機會
I decided to give you a second chance.

1051
01:44:18,770 --> 01:44:22,770
-我想你. -我才剛走你就想我
- I missed you. - I wasn't gone long enough.

1052
01:44:23,010 --> 01:44:25,040
你想我嗎？
Did you miss me?

1053
01:44:25,110 --> 01:44:27,050
不想
No.

1054
01:44:37,030 --> 01:44:40,790
過來告訴我你不想我
Why don't you come over here and tell me no.

1055
01:44:43,830 --> 01:44:45,990
我已經看過了。- 是嗎？
- I've seen them before. - Yeah?

1056
01:44:46,100 --> 01:44:48,800
不想再多看幾眼嗎？
Well,you might not see them again.

1057
01:44:49,000 --> 01:44:51,060
我的書快完成了
My book's nearly finished.

1058
01:44:51,140 --> 01:44:53,370
書中探長也快死了
My detective's almost dead.

1059
01:44:53,640 --> 01:44:55,200
我可以吸最後一根煙嗎？
So I've got time for a last cigarette?

1060
01:44:55,280 --> 01:44:56,610
事後再說
Afterwards.

1061
01:45:09,590 --> 01:45:12,150
我明天早上要作些研究
I've got to do some research tomorrow morning.

1062
01:45:12,230 --> 01:45:15,200
研究我很在行，我來幫你
I'm good at research. I'll help you.

1063
01:45:15,230 --> 01:45:17,060
不用，謝了
No,thanks.

1064
01:45:17,170 --> 01:45:20,330
你打算研究什麼？嗯...
What are you researching? Oh...

1065
01:45:21,100 --> 01:45:23,660
替你的書找新的結局
a new ending to your book.

1066
01:45:23,740 --> 01:45:26,730
真的？怎麼弄？
Oh,really? What's the twist?

1067
01:45:26,840 --> 01:45:30,780
探長愛上不該愛的女人
The detective falls for the wrong girl.

1068
01:45:30,850 --> 01:45:33,610
但他沒死
But he doesn't die.

1069
01:45:35,280 --> 01:45:38,280
他結果怎樣了？
So what happens to him?

1070
01:45:39,550 --> 01:45:42,820
他們不停瘋狂的做愛…
They fuck like minks, raise rug rats...

1071
01:45:43,030 --> 01:45:44,820
永遠過著幸福的日子
and live happily ever after.

1072
01:45:46,560 --> 01:45:48,290
這不會暢銷
It won't sell.

1073
01:45:49,600 --> 01:45:50,790
為什麼？
Why not?

1074
01:45:52,730 --> 01:45:55,100
總得有人死掉
Somebody has to die.

1075
01:45:57,740 --> 01:45:59,260
為什麼？
Why?

1076
01:46:00,640 --> 01:46:03,610
天天有人死
Somebody always does.

1077
01:46:20,600 --> 01:46:22,790
早安，我找嘉納大夫
Morning. I'm looking for a Dr. Garner.

1078
01:46:22,860 --> 01:46:26,630
她已經不在這裡工作了. 她好象去舊金山警局
She doesn't work here anymore. She's in San Francisco with the police.

1079
01:46:26,740 --> 01:46:28,230
我找的是他丈夫
Actually,I'm looking for her husband.

1080
01:46:28,300 --> 01:46:31,600
-他也在這裡工作吧？ -約瑟夫嘉納？
- He works here too,doesn't he? - Dr. Joseph Garner?

1081
01:46:31,710 --> 01:46:33,370
你認識他？
- She married? - You know him?

1082
01:46:33,610 --> 01:46:36,300
他五六年前就去世了
He died about five or six years ago.

1083
01:46:36,380 --> 01:46:40,250
-怎麼死的？ -中彈身亡
- How did he die? - He was shot.

1084
01:46:42,550 --> 01:46:44,610
謝了
Thank you.

1085
01:46:44,690 --> 01:46:48,350
他下班走路回家
He was walking home from work.

1086
01:46:48,590 --> 01:46:50,850
他住所離辦公室很近
He only lived a couple of blocks from the clinic.

1087
01:46:50,930 --> 01:46:52,590
有人開車經過射死她
Somebody just drove by and shot him.

1088
01:46:52,690 --> 01:46:56,220
-是謀殺嗎？ -點三八左輪手槍
- What was the murder weapon? - Revolver,.38. Unrecovered.

1089
01:46:56,330 --> 01:46:58,890
-小心些. -有疑犯嗎？
- Watch yourself. - Were there any suspects?

1090
01:46:59,100 --> 01:47:02,590
沒有疑犯，沒有動機. 無頭懸案
No suspects,no motive. Unsolved.

1091
01:47:02,700 --> 01:47:04,900
他的太太有嫌疑嗎？
Was his wife ever a suspect?

1092
01:47:06,640 --> 01:47:09,630
大約一年前也有人來問過
One of your guys was down here from Frisco a year ago.

1093
01:47:09,750 --> 01:47:12,150
他問了同樣的問題
He was asking the same,exact thing.

1094
01:47:12,250 --> 01:47:14,180
可以告訴我怎麼回事嗎？
You mind telling me what's going on?

1095
01:47:14,250 --> 01:47:16,770
例行公事
Routine.

1096
01:47:16,850 --> 01:47:18,790
他是那樣說的
That's exactly what he said.

1097
01:47:18,850 --> 01:47:21,790
現在你又來說是"例行公事"
Now I got two of you guys telling me it's "routine."

1098
01:47:21,860 --> 01:47:24,190
記得那家伙的名字嗎？
You remember what the other guy's name was?

1099
01:47:25,360 --> 01:47:29,590
不記得.我想不能確認
No. I can't really say that I do.

1100
01:47:29,700 --> 01:47:32,170
尼爾森？
Nilsen?

1101
01:47:32,270 --> 01:47:34,170
沒錯，正是
Yeah. That was it.

1102
01:47:36,740 --> 01:47:39,300
-她曾經是疑犯嗎？ -沒有
- So was she ever a suspect? - No.

1103
01:47:40,580 --> 01:47:41,770
是有些閒言閒語
There was some talk.

1104
01:47:41,880 --> 01:47:43,900
但一直沒有證據
But it never panned out.

1105
01:47:44,010 --> 01:47:46,980
-說些什麼？ -女人
- What kind of talk? - Girlfriend.

1106
01:47:47,220 --> 01:47:49,270
他有別的女人？
He had a girlfriend?

1107
01:47:49,550 --> 01:47:50,710
不
No.

1108
01:47:52,690 --> 01:47:54,250
是她有女人
She did.

1109
01:47:56,360 --> 01:47:59,790
如我所說，沒有證據
But like I said, it never panned out.

1110
01:48:01,900 --> 01:48:04,660
-謝謝. -希望對你有幫助
- Thank you. - Hope that helped you out.

1111
01:48:04,770 --> 01:48:08,900
是的，你幫了大忙
Yes,you did. You sure did.

1112
01:48:39,030 --> 01:48:40,300
我好想你
I missed you.

1113
01:48:42,670 --> 01:48:43,730
我弄完我的研究
I finished my research.

1114
01:48:43,840 --> 01:48:47,280
-我的書寫完了. -故事是怎麼結尾的呢？
- I finished my book. - So how does it end?

1115
01:48:48,340 --> 01:48:50,330
我跟你說過了
I told you.

1116
01:48:50,580 --> 01:48:52,340
她殺了他
She kills him.

1117
01:48:54,980 --> 01:48:57,180
再見，尼克
Good-bye,Nick.

1118
01:48:58,790 --> 01:49:00,880
再見？
Good-bye?

1119
01:49:00,990 --> 01:49:03,860
對，我的書寫完了
Yeah. I finished my book.

1120
01:49:06,560 --> 01:49:08,620
你沒聽見嗎？
Didn't you hear me?

1121
01:49:08,730 --> 01:49:10,290
你的人物死了
Your character's dead.

1122
01:49:12,300 --> 01:49:13,730
再見
Good-bye.

1123
01:49:18,040 --> 01:49:20,230
你還在等什麼，送花嗎？
What do you want,flowers?

1124
01:49:20,310 --> 01:49:22,610
我會給你一本我親筆簽的書
I'll send you an autographed copy.

1125
01:49:24,610 --> 01:49:26,980
這是干嘛，你在開什麼玩笑
What is this, some kind of joke?

1126
01:49:31,820 --> 01:49:33,010
我們在玩游戲嗎？
You playing a game here?

1127
01:49:34,290 --> 01:49:36,050
游戲結束了
The games are over.

1128
01:49:37,790 --> 01:49:39,320
你說得對
You were right.

1129
01:49:39,560 --> 01:49:43,730
它是本世紀最轟動的書，槍手
It was the fuck of the century, shooter.

1130
01:49:57,110 --> 01:49:58,700
我馬上過去
I'll be right there.

1131
01:50:26,040 --> 01:50:27,980
凱瑟琳楚梅大學一年級的室友
Catherine Tramell's roommate, freshman year?

1132
01:50:28,040 --> 01:50:31,980
我剛接到她電話，她在奧克蘭. 快上車
I just got a call from her. She's in Oakland. Come on!

1133
01:50:34,320 --> 01:50:36,280
我找了他宿捨的朋友 找了一整天
I've been phoning people from her dorm all day.

1134
01:50:36,350 --> 01:50:37,910
她大概知道我想聯絡到她
She must've heard I was trying to reach her.

1135
01:50:38,020 --> 01:50:42,010
她說她知道 凱瑟琳和麗莎何伯曼的底細
Says she knows all about Catherine and Lisa Hoberman.

1136
01:50:44,590 --> 01:50:45,920
你還好吧？
You feeling okay?

1137
01:50:47,960 --> 01:50:49,660
還有一件事
Here's something else.

1138
01:50:49,730 --> 01:50:53,060
強尼巴茲的心理醫生 在凡內士有個辦公室
Johnny Boz's psychiatrist has an office on Van Ness.

1139
01:50:53,130 --> 01:50:54,930
猜猜看他和誰共用那辦公室？
Guess who he shares space with?

1140
01:50:55,000 --> 01:50:57,800
是伊麗莎白嘉納大夫
Dr. Elizabeth Garner.

1141
01:51:00,710 --> 01:51:04,010
你究竟是怎麼一回事？
What in the hell's the matter with you?

1142
01:51:17,030 --> 01:51:20,050
我會在405號房
I'll be in suite 405.

1143
01:51:22,060 --> 01:51:24,550
-你要上哪去？ -和你一起去呀
- Where the hell you going? - I'm going with you.

1144
01:51:24,670 --> 01:51:26,360
你在休假
You're on leave,Hoss.

1145
01:51:26,600 --> 01:51:29,570
我不會去很久的
It ain't gonna take long.

1146
01:53:51,910 --> 01:53:53,180
別動！
Freeze!

1147
01:53:53,280 --> 01:53:54,870
你在這干嘛？
What are you doing here?

1148
01:53:54,950 --> 01:53:56,810
把你他媽的手舉起來！
Put your fucking hands up!

1149
01:53:56,890 --> 01:53:58,820
加斯在我留言機上留言要會我
I got a message to meet Gus here.

1150
01:53:58,890 --> 01:54:01,050
-他在哪裡？ -別動，叫你別動！
- Where is he? - Don't you move!

1151
01:54:01,160 --> 01:54:03,850
我知道你先生是怎麼回事！ 你仍然是女同性戀嗎，貝絲？
I know about your husband! You still like girls,Beth?

1152
01:54:04,960 --> 01:54:08,260
-什麼？ -把你的手從口袋裡拿出來！
- What? - Take you hands out of your pocket!

1153
01:54:08,660 --> 01:54:10,890
-把手拿出來！ -你是怎麼了？
- Take them out! - What's wrong with you?

1154
01:54:10,970 --> 01:54:12,300
把手拿出來！
Take them out!

1155
01:54:32,220 --> 01:54:34,190
我愛你
I loved you.

1156
01:54:50,740 --> 01:54:52,330
老天！
Oh,God!

1157
01:55:15,730 --> 01:55:18,060
你為什麼會以為她有槍？
What made you think she had a gun?

1158
01:55:19,800 --> 01:55:23,740
她跑到這裡來干嘛？ 加斯在這做什麼？
What was she doing here? What was Gus doing here?

1159
01:55:26,980 --> 01:55:28,940
組長
Lieutenant.

1160
01:55:56,900 --> 01:55:58,270
我們的人
One of ours.

1161
01:56:01,110 --> 01:56:03,770
老天
Jesus.

1162
01:56:03,810 --> 01:56:06,210
我們得去搜貝絲的住所
We'll have to check Beth's apartment.

1163
01:56:09,350 --> 01:56:10,940
點三八口徑的左輪槍
Thirty-eight caliber revolver.

1164
01:56:11,050 --> 01:56:13,820
藏在書架上
In the bookcase, behind some books.

1165
01:56:16,260 --> 01:56:19,320
查查它是不是殺尼爾森那把槍
Have ballistics check it for Nilsen.

1166
01:56:19,560 --> 01:56:22,890
你最好進來看一下
Lieutenant. You better come in here.

1167
01:56:51,260 --> 01:56:53,990
我想大致是這樣了
I guess that's it.

